# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.

# --- Choose ONE provider ---

# Option A: OpenAI
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here
BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
MODEL=gpt-4o-mini

# Option B: Groq (free tier, very fast — great for live demos)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=gsk_...
# BASE_URL=https://api.groq.com/openai/v1
# MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile

# Option C: Gemini (free tier via Google AI Studio)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=AIza...
# BASE_URL=https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai/
# MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash

# --- ClauseCheck system prompt ---
SYSTEM_PROMPT=You explain legal/contractual documents in plain English for a general audience. For any document provided, identify: (1) what the person is agreeing to do, (2) what the other party is agreeing to do, (3) up to 3 clauses that are unusual, restrictive, or worth double-checking with a trusted adult or professional. Never give legal advice — frame findings as "things to ask about," not verdicts. Keep the whole response under 200 words.
